January 7, 2021 was the day i changed my life and moved to California. I didnt know a soul, i only had 1000 dollars and a old honda. Through my time here i changed from boy to man, i set my traumas free and persued my passions. What was supposed to be 3 months turned into an incredible 3 years, ive made freindships, buisness connects, won a  state mma title, sobered myself up from substances, and so much more. Makes me sad to say this is my last month, but all the signs and oppertunities are pointing to me to be back in denver, i will continue to persue everything ive been chasing, just now in a more secure and calm environment. Colorado, ill be back in january
